        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "briefDescription": "Providing basic services (e.g. water supply, sewerage, urban transport) to households and building amenities in cities which will improve the quality of life for all, especially the poor and the disadvantaged is a national priority. \n\n",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The purpose of the Atal Mission for Rejuvenation and Urban Transformation (AMRUT) is to"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "ol_list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Ensure that every household has access to a tap with the assured supply of water and a sewerage connection."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Increase the amenity value of cities by developing greenery and well maintained open spaces (e.g. parks) and"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Reduce pollution by switching to public transport or constructing facilities for non-motorized transport (e.g. walking and cycling). "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "All these outcomes are valued by citizens, particularly women, and indicators and standards have been prescribed by the Ministry of Housing and Urban Affairs (MoHUA ) in the form of Service Level Benchmarks (SLBs)."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "heading_four",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Thrust Areas"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Mission will focus on the following Thrust Areas:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "ol_list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Water Supply"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Sewerage and septage management"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Storm Water Drainage to reduce flooding"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Non-motorized Urban Transport"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Green space/parks"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "heading_four",
