          "process": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "The applicant need not apply for the scheme."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Projects will be executed by Urban Local Bodies (ULBs). "
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "In case the ULBs do not have adequate capacity to handle projects, the State Government may recommend in State Annual Action Plan (SAAP), upon a Resolution passed by the ULB, for the execution of the projects by specialized parastatal agencies of the State or Central Governments. Such arrangements should necessarily be executed by way of a tripartite Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) amongst the State Government, the specialized Parastatal agencies and the concerned Municipality. "
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "In such a case, the capacity of the ULBs will be augmented through the capacity-building component of the AMRUT. The maintenance and upkeep of the created assets will be the responsibility of the ULB and the State Government. "
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": ""
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
